Package gov.usgs.anss.metadata

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckDatalessDirectory
    This looks through the DATALESS directory for files which are not mentioned in the SEEDURLs in the metadata.channel table.
    IRCode
    IRCode.java - An IR code basically contains the IRCODE and all of its aliases.
    LoadURL
    This class uses FTP and HTTP to gather dataless volumes from originators.
    MetaData
    This class is the thread that manages the metadata in memory cache of the data.
    MetaDataServer
    This class is the main() class for the MetaDataServer.
    NormalizedToMeta
    This class takes the normalized tables (station, channel, and response) and puts the data in the meta-data server ready non-normalized tables (channelmeta, channelepoch).
    SeedDumpToMetaData
    This class processes a file dumped from rdseed -s into a SEEDStation and SEEDChannel representation and looks for problems.
    WebdcSetup
    File write out various files needed by the WebDC or arclink scripts.
